@startuml FUSE_Batch_IO_Opt_Timeline
skinparam sequence {
    Participant BackgroundColor #f0f8ff
    Actor BackgroundColor #ffe4e1
}

actor "业务进程" as BusinessApp
participant "FUSE内核驱动" as FUSE_Kernel
participant "ulogfs(FUSE用户态)" as Ulogfs
participant "tmpfs文件系统" as TmpFS
participant "logtail(inotify采集)" as LogTail

== 模式1：FUSE默认参数（无批量、无内核缓存）==
note over BusinessApp
每个小write单独触发一次FUSE回调，频繁上下文切换
end note

loop 3次连续小日志write
    BusinessApp -> FUSE_Kernel: write(小日志片段)【用户→内核 切换】
    FUSE_Kernel -> Ulogfs: fuse_write单次回调【内核→用户 切换】
    Ulogfs -> TmpFS: pwrite写入小数据
    TmpFS --> Ulogfs: 写入完成
    Ulogfs -> FUSE_Kernel: fuse_reply_write
    FUSE_Kernel --> BusinessApp: write返回
    TmpFS -> LogTail: inotify MODIFY细碎事件
end loop

note over FUSE_Kernel
每次getattr/lookup都穿透到ulogfs
end note

BusinessApp -> FUSE_Kernel: stat获取文件属性
FUSE_Kernel -> Ulogfs: getattr回调
Ulogfs -> TmpFS: stat底层文件
TmpFS --> Ulogfs: 属性返回
Ulogfs -> FUSE_Kernel: 回复属性
FUSE_Kernel --> BusinessApp: stat返回

== 模式2：内核批量IO+元数据缓存优化模式 ==
note over BusinessApp
3次连续小write内核合并为1次FUSE回调，元数据走内核缓存
end note

loop 3次连续小日志write
    BusinessApp -> FUSE_Kernel: write(小日志片段)
end loop
note over FUSE_Kernel: batch_write聚合为128KB大块IO，内核排队缓冲
FUSE_Kernel -> Ulogfs: 单次fuse_write下发合并后大块数据【仅1次上下文切换】
Ulogfs -> TmpFS: 单次大块pwrite写入
TmpFS --> Ulogfs: 批量写入完成
Ulogfs -> FUSE_Kernel: fuse_reply_write
FUSE_Kernel --> BusinessApp: 全部write依次返回
TmpFS -> LogTail: 单次inotify MODIFY事件

note over FUSE_Kernel
entry/attr缓存命中，直接内核返回，不进入ulogfs
end note

BusinessApp -> FUSE_Kernel: stat获取文件属性
FUSE_Kernel --> BusinessApp: 内核缓存直接返回属性，无用户态切换
@enduml